The paper discusses secure multi-party computation (MPC) on big data, which is a topic related to both cryptography (cs.CR) and databases (cs.DB). The paper also mentions data-parallel processing (cs.DC) and optimizations (cs.PL), which are relevant sub-categories. Finally, the use of hybrid protocols and the focus on scalability suggest that the paper could also be classified under distributed systems (cs.DS).
